** Mid Level Android Developers   
  
** My client in the financial services industry is looking for an Android developer to join on a 10 month contract starting as soon as possible. The role will include working for a tight-knit team where you will be taking ownership of the Android product.   
  
To be successful in this role you must have:  

  * Experience in contactless payments integration 
  * Other 3rd party payments integration including Visa & MasterCard 
  * Minimum 3 years' experience with Android development using Kotlin 
  * The ability to take charge of the app and make decisions where necessary 
  * Excellent written and verbal communication skills, and the ability to communicate with internal and external stakeholders 
  * Strong time management skills 
  
Interviews happening now as they are keen to have someone start next week or
the week after. Day rate is up to $550 depending on your experience. You must
be based in either Brisbane, Sydney or Melbourne.  
  
